  "detailed_description": "<h1>Share the Voxels!</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Modding Support</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/5fd5bbc12066f15571f3afec8dd1d693.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/5fd5bbc12066f15571f3afec8dd1d693.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/5fd5bbc12066f15571f3afec8dd1d693.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom maps, pistols, rifles, knives/axes, attachments, and more—then publish them to the Steam Workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The SDK and modding guide is inside the game folder and includes walkthroughs to help you get started.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is just the beginning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game will be supported with additional updates adding more items, levels and features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel Project offers an immersive sandbox experience set in a fully destructible voxel environment. Explore a dynamic world teeming with vehicles, dynamic fire mechanics, enemy NPCs, voxel gore, weapon customization, and a bunch of additional features to discover. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sandbox Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock boundless creativity with unrestricted access to props and weapons, all with unlimited ammo. Explosives, guns, cars, props, NPCs, etc. Utilize your tablet to spawn and manipulate elements, toggling between day and night settings or turning off the NPC AI to prevent them from moving </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Siege Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend against waves of advancing enemies in this intense siege experience, playable in either day or night mode. Fortify your position with barricades and leverage the environment to your advantage. Earn currency to upgrade your gear and buy barricades, with nighttime gameplay offering greater rewards. Loot ammo from defeated foes, and choose your approach: move stealthily with silencers and stay hidden, or go all out</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Game Tools & Mechanics</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spawn Menu</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Customization</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify weapons with a ton of different attachments </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Impact Driver</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can screw any objects together. Build anything. The only limit is your imagination</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destructible Vehicles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel project features completely destructible vehicles. Cut off the roof with a plasma saber and make a convertible. Tie objects or ragdolls to the car and drag them across the map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Fire</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set everything on fire and watch it burn, or try to extinguish it to save what’s left </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics Gun</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate objects using physics-based interactions </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voxel Gore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demolish Ragdolls down to the last voxel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more features that will be added in the future with updates! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Song: Slowboy, Rizó & NØCTRIS - Sold Dreams [NCS Release]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Release Trailer Song: ANGELPLAYA - DANGEROUS [NCS Release]</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is just the beginning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game will be supported with additional updates adding more items, levels and features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel Project offers an immersive sandbox experience set in a fully destructible voxel environment. Explore a dynamic world teeming with vehicles, dynamic fire mechanics, enemy NPCs, voxel gore, weapon customization, and a bunch of additional features to discover. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sandbox Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock boundless creativity with unrestricted access to props and weapons, all with unlimited ammo. Explosives, guns, cars, props, NPCs, etc. Utilize your tablet to spawn and manipulate elements, toggling between day and night settings or turning off the NPC AI to prevent them from moving </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/796e0c33b1c203dffa6b7acc682d1652.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/6b3b9a97bc285813b944be2c549b5ada.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c1678f75b90c5a8c0567dcc5fb90889a.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Siege Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend against waves of advancing enemies in this intense siege experience, playable in either day or night mode. Fortify your position with barricades and leverage the environment to your advantage. Earn currency to upgrade your gear and buy barricades, with nighttime gameplay offering greater rewards. Loot ammo from defeated foes, and choose your approach: move stealthily with silencers and stay hidden, or go all out</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/c85497d300c405df6fe4dfc4054bafc1.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a149f50c1fd5f6847ed1988a64e3b5ff.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Game Tools & Mechanics</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spawn Menu</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9b20c344be837ccb64d8b20e1c1890c7.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapon Customization</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify weapons with a ton of different attachments </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/df1875be7f6a56828ae2b979067ce70c.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Impact Driver</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can screw any objects together. Build anything. The only limit is your imagination</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2bb52b4e4f5bf2680a9f86013b93240.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Destructible Vehicles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voxel project features completely destructible vehicles. Cut off the roof with a plasma saber and make a convertible. Tie objects or ragdolls to the car and drag them across the map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/e2162e5cb5b607412b7dd6cb9cccf199.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Fire</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set everything on fire and watch it burn, or try to extinguish it to save what’s left </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/9bf3957bf1e69febb9d9a381d146343a.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics Gun</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manipulate objects using physics-based interactions </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/a29ea519243314bb24758862c33b6873.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voxel Gore</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Demolish Ragdolls down to the last voxel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0eee871d802a708c73a041d2cb0a2fe7.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.poster.avif?t=1774377804\" width=400 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.webm?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2858370/extras/0022203e59f775c6b5c8f310706681b8.mp4?t=1774377804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more features that will be added in the future with updates! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trailer Song: Slowboy, Rizó & NØCTRIS - Sold Dreams [NCS Release]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Release Trailer Song: ANGELPLAYA - DANGEROUS [NCS Release]</p>",
